cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on human pose estimation/tracking using deep learning-based models. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is also likely as the paper uses 3D graphical engines to synthesize large scale labeled training datasets. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category as the paper proposes a semi-supervised data augmentation approach for training deep learning-based models. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also possible as the paper uses AI techniques for human pose estimation/tracking. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with generating synthetic human pose datasets using 3D scans.
